title: EZREAL JUNGLE

embed.description: New video fro you guys. This is my take on the new Ezreal Jungle in Patch 7.17. I talk about Runes, Masteries, Builds and Style of Play for Ezreal Jungle. Make sure if you enjoyed this video to leave a Like and a Comment down below.

body: Hey guys, let me know what you think of my latest video. It's a small guide ot Ezreal jungle. give me some feedback on my video and on whether you think ezreal jungle can work!
